item.title: Error help
item.dc:creator: @verbios verbios
item.description:
@verbios wrote:

First error: Could you, by chance, already have a method with a name “ifFreeze”?

Second error: You declared the method to return a type of “void”, or basically, declared it so it doesn’t return a value. You would have to make it boolean type in order to return a value of either “true” or “false”.
